title: Delirium Tremens (Heart Core Soundtrack)
tags: 1997 2004 AGA Amiga Breakpoint Demo TCP video
info:
Released at the TCP party 1997 in Copenhagen. I think I was ranked 2nd with this module, and received quite a lot of positive feedback on it.

Tune was later re-used in Heart Core by IRIS, released at Breakpoint 2004.
